storyInfo: Team Rainbow makes a deep incursion into an abandoned laboratory in the Ural Mountains, preparing to capture the mad scientist, Levi Klitschko. What they find defies all expectations.

attributes.content: We've arrived at Magnethill No. 2. Repeat, we've arrived at Magnethill No. 2.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Iana, Ela, report the situation on your end, over.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Business as usual. Just putting in the finishing touches.
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: If the intel we got is correct, this should be the last batch!
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: We'll head towards you after we clean up over here!
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: Just sit back and leave it to the Poles.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: I already hear the sound of Grzmot mines going off. They'll be just fine.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: And you, Blitz, you're supposed to be doing your job. Namely, standing guard.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Pay attention to the meter's readout. The intel shows that there's nuclear waste sealed inside this building.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Frost, how far until our objective?
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: After we pass through the checkpoint and the storage room, the main laboratory should be right there.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: The drones showed that the mercenaries set up some simple fortifications at and around the checkpoint.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: No bunkers, no dead ends. The entrance has been sealed shut, and they've laid a lot of barbed wire all around.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: Nine. Their rough positions have been marked on the team terminal.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: The entrance of the long corridor leading from the checkpoint into the storage room has been completely sealed, and the drones haven't been able to get in any farther.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: Okay, I'll take care of this.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Do you have any suggestions, Lord?
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: I still have some extra incendiary rounds. How many do you need?
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: The checkpoint entrance's full of obstacles. Blow it up, and the rubble's just going to be in the way.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Here's the plan. We'll blast the ceiling and the wall on the right. One of us will rappel in from the top and provide cover fire. The rest of us will breach from the right side.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Frost, you're on cover fire and support.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Once the charges go off, Tachanka, drop a grenade from up top. The rest of us will throw flashbangs at the designated locations.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: On the ground, we'll head inside in this order: Blitz, Ash, Tachanka. Look alive out there. Don't let this opportunity slip away.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: If you have any questions, it's now or never.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: You all ready? Good. Take position.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Frost, on your mark, that's when we'll begin.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: I'll provide cover fire. The rest of you, move up!
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Blitz, stay alert. Tachanka, use the drone and check out the hallway and the storage room's status.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: How is it looking up ahead?
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: The storage room was filled with ammo and supplies. They had been stationed here for some time.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: There are no hostiles in the storage room. Just black crystals on some petri dishes.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: What's this stuff inside the cans?
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: Glowing mineral crystals. Never seen them before.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Minerals. Composites. As long as they are glowing, they might be radioactive.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Don't worry. Geiger's not reacting to anything.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: Then let's leave them be and go straight in.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Time's a wasting, team. Let's move.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: We have just taken care of the enemy, but they have blocked the corridor passage with a lot of obstacles.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: We have to take a different route to the core, over.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: We're about to head inside the main laboratory. I need you to come back us up ASAP, over.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: What now? Shall we wait for them?
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: No, time is pressing. Keep going.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Up ahead is the main laboratory.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: Stay alert. Subdue the target when you have them in sight.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: There's no one here, just these strange machines.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: Don't let your guard down. The lab equipment's running, which means the target is still here.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Then we need to head inside the real laboratory.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: This here is the control room. You see the machines on the other side of that window? That's where the actual experiments happen.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Stay alert... We don't know how many hostiles we have here.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: I see unwelcome friends will always invite themselves in.
attributes.name: Levi

attributes.content: (Looks like we're the only ones here.)
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: Put your hands up, Dr. Levi. Move away from the terminal.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: And here I was wondering how much longer it would take you to show up.
attributes.name: Levi

attributes.content: Did you take out my security detail? What a shame.
attributes.name: Levi

attributes.content: I cut them their last paycheck just yesterday.
attributes.name: Levi

attributes.content: Well, I ask you to be careful with the things here. They can be delicate.
attributes.name: Levi

attributes.content: Don't even try to do anything funny. This charade is over.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Over? My new experiment has just started.
attributes.name: Levi

attributes.content: Stop what you're doing... This is your last warning.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Hahahahaha, and what if I refuse?
attributes.name: Levi

attributes.content: What's the matter? Are you afraid of a senile, defenseless ordinary citizen?
attributes.name: Levi

attributes.content: You are the chief scientist of the Magnethill No. 2 laboratory, Levi Klitschko.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Stay away from the equipment. I know exactly what you're trying to do.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: I've got to hand it to you. Your team works fast.
attributes.name: Levi

attributes.content: There's nothing you can do to stop it, but do feel free to fire your weapons.
attributes.name: Levi

attributes.content: If it wasn't for those shortsighted, useless morons getting in my way again and again...
attributes.name: Levi

attributes.content: I would've finished all of this twenty years ago.
attributes.name: Levi

attributes.content: You have no idea what you are doing.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: The equipment in this lab is in disrepair, and you are creating a nuclear contamination disaster!
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Of course I know what I am doing.
attributes.name: Levi

attributes.content: The road of exploratory science is a treacherous one.
attributes.name: Levi

attributes.content: Yet it's a road worth taking. Roads that lead to the truth are always worth taking.
attributes.name: Levi

attributes.content: All I am doing now is getting the results I should've had twenty years ago, and no one has the right to stop me.
attributes.name: Levi

attributes.content: Uh, just complaining a little bit about the close miss just now.
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: We could've regrouped with the rest of the team at the main lab!
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: No, it's coming from the lab!
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: Get your Replicator ready. They might be in trouble.
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: Wh-What the hell's this? ! Where's everyone?
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: Where's the map? What's with this huge hole?
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: There's no problem with the map. The main lab should be behind this door.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: I'm just giving her pressure points a few presses to help patch her up.
...After that madman activated his equipment, the whole lab was swept by a huge shockwave.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: The target activated that weird device of his, and we all got knocked out by the blast.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: And after we came around, well, this is it.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: We don't have any signal, so we can't contact Ela and Iana.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: The only thing I am sure about is we definitely aren't anywhere near the mission area.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: It's hardly the most precise way to put it, but it's like we were... teleported... somewhere with the whole lab.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: She's right. It's like we were suddenly launched by a rocket to the moon and that's not a joke.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.text: Through a huge crack in the wall, all one can see outside the house is a desolate desert. As if the house had fallen from the sky to the desert.

attributes.content: If Levi Klitschko was swept by the shockwave too, he'd probably be in a similar situation.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: We'll rest up first. I'll plan our next steps.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Good news first. The supplies for those mercenaries have been thrown in with us, so at least for a short time ammo won't be an issue.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Eyes open! There's something outside coming toward us!
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: It sounds like some sort of heavy machinery... but it's way too fast!
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: *Profanity* We're in big trouble! Prepare for battle!
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Have you ever seen an arthropod as big as a small car?
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Normal bullets aren't going to penetrate its husk!
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: If we let that thing tear the control room's wall down, it's all over for us! !
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: But shooting its legs isn't stopping it!
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Let it bring the wall down!
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: I'm fine. It's just my shield's busted.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: It took a good bite out of the wall.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: Let's be sure to take its husk down when we get our payback.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: I'm not sure we can call it a plan, but it's the only choice we have.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Your ammo is the only thing we have that's doing any damage to that thing. Plus my breaching rounds, maybe.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: We'll take him down the moment he breaches the wall.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Judging by the damage AP's done on that thing, the breaching round should take its leg down. Hopefully that'll give us a clean view of its underside.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: After that, it's going to be all you.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: If any of you has a better idea, I'm all ears.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Ahh, finally time to take a breather.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: Like, you know, the planet we all know about?
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: But we need to prepare for the worst.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: With the wall collapsed, we can't even use this place as shelter.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Let's get moving. At least until we find another place to hunker down.
attributes.name: Ash
